(114, 'Up in the Air', 22947, '', 'movie', 2.068036, '/skp6h2el5rsaRmlzBhWZ6ZPyW2i.jpg', 'en', 'Up in the Air', 'George Clooney plays the dry cynical character of Ryan Bingham, an executive who specializes in \"downsizing\". Ryan lives out of his suitcase, traveling the country for the sole purpose terminating unwanted employees day after day. Just as Ryan is about to reach his life-long goal of the ten million mile frequent flyer mark some major changes come his way. Changes that threaten to crack the cold heartless exterior that is Ryan Bingham.', '18,10749,', '2009-09-05', '2017-06-21 07:53:33', '2017-06-21 07:53:33'),
