(751, 'Alone in the Dark', 12142, '', NULL, 3.117693, '/3HsprIjUEwYfnlEf7jumGm037Bk.jpg', 'en', 'Alone in the Dark', 'Edward Carnby is a private investigator specializing in unexplainable supernatural phenomena. His cases delve into the dark corners of the world, searching for truth in the occult remnants of ancient civilizations. Now, the greatest mystery of his past is about to become the most dangerous case he has ever faced.', '28,14,27,53,', '2005-01-28', '2017-07-13 11:03:22', '2017-07-13 11:03:22'),
(752, 'The Brothers Grimm', 4442, '', NULL, 3.116742, '/g6EgJUwwQre5RsvFj2hDsLzXUsH.jpg', 'en', 'The Brothers Grimm', 'Folklore collectors and con artists, Jake and Will Grimm, travel from village to village pretending to protect townsfolk from enchanted creatures and performing exorcisms. However, they are put to the test  when they encounter a real magical curse in a haunted forest with real magical beings, requiring genuine courage.', '12,14,28,35,53,', '2005-08-25', '2017-07-13 11:03:25', '2017-07-13 11:03:25'),
