(921, 'Stand Up Guys', 121824, '', NULL, 2.775285, '/pitHkpmZqGlfyRnm2nssoRXYSGa.jpg', 'en', 'Stand Up Guys', 'After serving 28 years in prison for accidentally killing the son of a crime boss, newly paroled gangster Val reunites with his former partners in crime, Doc and Hirsch, for a night on the town. As the three men revisit old haunts, reflect on their glory days and try to make up for lost time, one wrestles with a terrible quandary: Doc has orders to kill Val, and time is running out for him to figure out a way out of his dilemma.', '53,35,28,', '2013-01-31', '2017-07-13 11:11:26', '2017-07-13 11:11:26'),
