(1685, 'Sukiyaki Western Django', 13637, '', NULL, 1.901216, '/x97kmv4pBODtkws4XqSC4vilaCW.jpg', 'ja', 'Sukiyaki Western Django', 'Several hundred years after the Battle of Dannoura, the Genji and Heike clans face off again in a poor mountain town with a buried treasure legend. A revolver-wielding stranger, a lone gunman, burdened with emotional scars and blessed with incredible skill, drifts into town and crosses paths with two warring clans who are both on the hunt for a hidden treasure in a remote western town. Knowing his services are valuable to either side, he offers himself to the clan who will offer up the largest share of the wealth.  Yoshitsune commands his Genji gang in white while Kiyomori leads his Heike gang in red. Expectations collide as the key players wonder which gang the gunman will join. Dirty tricks, betrayal, desire and finally, love, get jumbled together, as the situation erupts into a showdown.', '12,28,35,37,53,', '2007-09-15', '2017-07-13 11:47:13', '2017-07-13 11:47:13'),
(1686, 'Catch a Fire', 1123, '', NULL, 1.900387, '/3gra6N7DUNdac8iG44ozl8Rnh8H.jpg', 'en', 'Catch a Fire', 'The true story of anti-apartheid activists in South Africa, and particularly the life of Patrick Chamusso, a timid foreman at Secunda CTL, the largest synthetic fuel plant in the world. Patrick is wrongly accused, imprisoned and tortured for an attempt to bomb the plant, with the injustice transforming the apolitical worker into a radicalised insurgent, who then carries out his own successful sabotage mission.', '28,18,53,', '2006-10-27', '2017-07-13 11:47:14', '2017-07-13 11:47:14'),
(1687, 'Maximum Overdrive', 9980, '', NULL, 1.899342, '/lgNXAQ1TlKEKzssbjcc5iEhs8mi.jpg', 'en', 'Maximum Overdrive', 'When a comet passes close to the earth, machines all over the world come alive and go on homicidal rampages. A group of people at a desolate truck stop are held hostage by a gang of homicidal 18-wheelers. The frightened people set out to defeat the killer machines ... or be killed by them.', '28,18,27,878,', '1986-07-25', '2017-07-13 11:47:18', '2017-07-13 11:47:18'),
